Module thomasmccue.dbclientappreal
Package thomasmccue.dbclientapp.model

Class ContactAppts

java.lang.Object
thomasmccue.dbclientapp.model.ContactAppts
public class ContactAppts extends Object
This class represents a ContactAppts object, an object that is essentially a truncated version of an Appointment, with only the variables needed to display in the contact schedule report.
